high_descs: Turn around so that you are facing the coffee pot and toaster.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter, by the coffee pot.
Turn around and walk towards the stove, stopping at the green bucket on the floor, by the stove, and under the window.
Cut the tomato in the green bucket into slices.
Place the knife in the green bucket.
Pick up one of the slices of tomato.
Turn to your left and walk past the windows, straight across the room, to the wooden shelf.
Place the tomato slice onto a plate from the shelf.
Pick up the plate with the tomato slice on it.
Turn around and walk across the room, past the stove, then turn right at the dishwasher and proceed to the refrigerator.
Place the plate with the tomato on it in the refrigerator, beside the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a tomato slice on it, in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right, then right again to face the coffee maker and knife.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn around then face the green trash can to your right.
Slice the tomato in the green trash can.
Put the knife in the green trash can.
Take a slice of tomato from the green trash can.
Turn left and head towards the brown shelves in front of you.
Put the tomato slice on the plate on the brown shelves.
Take the plate with the tomato slice from the brown shelves.
Turn around, then right and head towards the fridge.
Place the plate with the tomato slice in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a tomato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the stove.
Hang a right and walk to the coffee maker with a yellow-handled knife on it, pick up the knife.
Turn to your left and walk to the green bin at the left side of the stove.
Slice the tomato that is in the green bin.
Place the knife in the bin to the left of the tomato.
Pick up the center slice of the tomato.
Turn to your left and walk to the brown rack against the wall.
Place the tomato slice in the bowl on the second shelf from the bottom.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato in it.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on it, hang a right to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the bowl with the tomato on the shelf to the right of the tomato and apple, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a tomato slice in a bowl

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the oven then make another right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is on the counter top.
Turn around with the knife and walk forward to a green bin. Turn right to face it.
Slice the tomato that is in the green bin.
Place the knife inside the green bin.
Pick up one slice of the tomato.
Turn left and walk over to the shelf with the tomato slice.
Place the tomato slice inside the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato slice from the shelf.
Turn to the right and walk forward with the bowl.Turn right again and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the bowl with the tomato slice inside the refrigerator and close it.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of tomato in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the yellow handled knife.
Turn around and walk past the stove then turn right and walk to the green garbage.
Cut the tomato in the garbage into slices.
Put the knife in the green garbage.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk to the shelves then take a step to your right.
Put the tomato in the clear bowl that's on the shelves in front of you.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato in it.
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk almost to the counter then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a tomato in it in the fridge.
